 at the stock's technicals to evaluate its outlook. In the below technical analysis, I determine that the chart, moving averages, and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1339907231/image_1339907231.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741650-verizon-has-ominous-clouds-on-the-horizon-technical-analysis", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 11:03:50"}, {"id": "4741649", "title": "XLU: Utility Stocks Have Just Begun Their AI-Driven Ascent", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"high voltage post.\" data-id=\"480406477\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4256px\" height=\"2832px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/480406477/image_480406477.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hxdyl</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"i