20share.\" target=\"_blank\"><span>the time</span></a><span> of its Initial Public Offering (\"IPO\") on March 10, 2021 has likely been highly disappointed in the stock's performance and regretted the day they bought it. The stock is down nearly 50% since the</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1355025074/image_1355025074.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741644-coupangs-emerging-opportunities-a-compelling-case-for-investment", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 10:44:17"}, {"id": "4741641", "title": "Atkore Is In The Down Portion Of A Black-Swan-Boom/Could-Be-Worse-Bust Cycle", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"High Angle View Of Swans Swimming In Lake\" data-id=\"962884198\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NejauPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Black swans aren\u2019t what they used to be.</p> <p>When ancient Roman satirist <a href=\"https://www.gutenberg.org/files/50657/50657-h/50657-h.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Juvenal coined the term</a> in the second century C.E., he was characterizing the perfect love interest. The idea was that black swans don\u2019t exist.</p> <p>Surprise!</p> <p>In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/962884198/image_962884198.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741641-atkore-stock-down-portion-of-black-swan-boom-be-worse-bust-cycle", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 10:32:17"}, {"id": "4741640", "title": "SCHO: Why I'm Writing About 4 Dollars", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Labrador puppy outdoors\" data-id=\"1354007887\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Uwe Krejci</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I've been doing some research on ETFs that hold short-term treasuries. I find these investments can be very useful as a way to store my cash in between what I would consider real investments. It's basically an opportunity to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354007887/image_1354007887.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741640-scho-etf-good-expense-ratio-but-high-duration-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 10:09:26"}, {"id": "4741639", "title": "DFEN: Too Risky Right Now", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/498381212/image_498381212.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Military Jets in Flight\" data-id=\"498381212\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/498381212/image_498381212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/498381212/image_498381212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/498381212/image_498381212.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/498381212/image_498381212.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/498381212/image_498381212.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/498381212/image_498381212.jpg?io=getty-c-w480